Always follow AGENTS.md and CLAUDE.md.

This repository is exclusively for the Velarro Estate website.

Never write production UI code unless the user explicitly provides:
START VELARRO IMPLEMENTATION

Build module by module and PR by PR.

Before visual implementation:
- Extract Figma section/page data with Figma MCP.
- Use section-level nodes when full-page nodes timeout.
- Ask the user for every required image URL before coding that page/section.
- Do not invent images, copy, products, prices, legal text, policies, routes, or interactions.

For visual pages:
- Match Figma exactly at 1440px first.
- Build feature by feature, section by section, layer by layer inside each section.
- Use existing project tokens and patterns before adding new values.
- Record Figma node IDs and source assumptions in docs.

Before claiming completion:
- Run npm run lint.
- Run npm run test.
- Run npm run build.
- Run npm run test:e2e -- --list.
- Report changed files, test results, and open assumptions.

Do not modify unrelated modules.
Do not bypass failing tests.
Do not push directly to main.
